sudo groupadd projectteam
sudo chown root:projectteam /tmp/projectgrp

Task 6: Apply SGID
sudo chmod 2775 /tmp/projectgrp

Task 7: Verify
ls -ld /tmp/projectgrp
â–¶ Output shows rwxrwsr-x (small s in group section)

Task 8: Test SGID effect
